        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 2. Syllis maganda n. sp. Paratypes (MNCN 16.01/18687). Scanning Electron Micrographs (A, B, D), digital camera (C). A), C) specimen of Haplosyllis sp. (arrows) which is feeding on a posterior dorsal cirrus of Syllis maganda n. sp. B) detail of simple chaeta of Haplosyllis sp. D) regeneration of the prostomium (arrow) of Syllis maganda n. sp., ventral view. No scale bar in digital camera photo." ;
